00:30:43.510 --> 00:30:46.305
Look. I don't know what
you're thinking. but you're not helping.

257
00:30:46.513 --> 00:30:48.640
There is no way I would ever
harm my own daughter.

258
00:30:48.849 --> 00:30:51.185
How do I even know
she is your daughter?

259
00:30:51.393 --> 00:30:52.811
Come on.

260
00:30:57.774 --> 00:30:59.484
What the hell?

261
00:31:35.562 --> 00:31:37.272
Okay.

262
00:31:37.481 --> 00:31:39.691
Now do you see
what I'm talking about?

263
00:31:39.900 --> 00:31:41.527
Will you take these handcuffs
off me?

264
00:31:41.735 --> 00:31:44.112
No. Get walking.

265
00:31:44.321 --> 00:31:46.949
There's a fire-lookout tower
on the far side of Toluca Lake.

266
00:31:47.157 --> 00:31:49.868
- It should have a radio.
- Fuck you. you stupid cop.

267
00:31:50.536 --> 00:31:53.372
This place is completely cut off.

268
00:31:54.206 --> 00:31:56.667
- You have no idea what's going on.
- Hey!

269
00:31:57.835 --> 00:31:59.962
Hey. you up there!

270
00:32:01.171 --> 00:32:03.257
I'm a police officer!

271
00:32:07.386 --> 00:32:09.054
What's going on?

272
00:32:16.728 --> 00:32:18.564
What is that?

273
00:32:23.026 --> 00:32:24.403
Stand back.

274
00:32:27.906 --> 00:32:30.325
Jesus Christ. shoot it.

275
00:32:43.338 --> 00:32:44.840
Stay where you are!

276
00:32:46.550 --> 00:32:48.051
Stop!

277
00:34:40.956 --> 00:34:41.957
Sharon!

278
00:36:11.421 --> 00:36:13.173
<i>Rose.</i>

279
00:36:32.818 --> 00:36:35.028
<i>Mrs. Da Silva.
I am an officer of the law...</i>

280
00:36:35.237 --> 00:36:37.156
<i>... and I will take you to safety.</i>

281
00:36:37.364 --> 00:36:40.200
<i>Mrs. Da Silva.
I am an officer of the law...</i>

282
00:36:40.409 --> 00:36:42.369
<i>... and I will take you to safety.</i>

283
00:36:42.578 --> 00:36:45.289
- Why don't you let me do that?
- Ninety percent of the time...

284
00:36:45.497 --> 00:36:46.832
...when a wife takes a run...

285
00:36:47.040 --> 00:36:49.293
...she takes the daughter
to a place like this...

286
00:36:49.501 --> 00:36:51.503
...I'd say she's damn mad
at her husband.

287
00:36:53.172 --> 00:36:55.465
You like hauling skeletons
out of your family closet?

288
00:36:55.674 --> 00:36:59.094
No. not all the time. but we're
driving on top of them right now.

289
00:36:59.303 --> 00:37:01.722
Coal fire's still burning
underneath.

290
00:37:01.930 --> 00:37:03.807
You see the barbershop over there?

291
00:37:04.308 --> 00:37:06.852
- Used to be my father's.
- Your father?

292
00:37:08.353 --> 00:37:10.105
He's dead.

293
00:37:10.522 --> 00:37:12.858
November '74.
when the fire caught.

294
00:37:13.066 --> 00:37:16.403
They tried to evacuate this place
as quick as they could...

295
00:37:16.612 --> 00:37:19.573
...but it was hellish. people were
dying and disappearing.

296
00:37:19.781 --> 00:37:22.451
Hell. they couldn't even find
half the bodies.

297
00:37:22.659 --> 00:37:24.244
That was the end of Silent Hill.

298
00:37:24.453 --> 00:37:27.664
These were good people.
most of them.

299
00:37:27.915 --> 00:37:30.209
Some. you might say deserved it.

300
00:37:30.417 --> 00:37:31.960
A little bit.

301
00:37:47.851 --> 00:37:49.770
Sharon!

302
00:39:21.403 --> 00:39:22.654
Sharon.

303
00:39:27.034 --> 00:39:28.327
Where are you hiding?

304
00:39:39.421 --> 00:39:43.926
<i>Burn the witch! Burn the witch!
Burn the witch!</i>

305
00:39:46.178 --> 00:39:48.055
Alessa Gillespie.

306
00:39:49.389 --> 00:39:50.641
Hey!

307
00:39:55.229 --> 00:39:56.396
Hey!

308
00:39:59.316 --> 00:40:00.359
Wait!

309
00:41:04.965 --> 00:41:06.633
It's okay.

310
00:41:08.802 --> 00:41:10.846
It's gonna be okay.

311
00:41:14.141 --> 00:41:16.560
I promise I'm gonna help you.

312
00:43:06.461 --> 00:43:07.921
Come on.

313
00:43:08.463 --> 00:43:10.299
Oh. God.

314
00:43:10.674 --> 00:43:12.217
Come on.

315
00:43:17.598 --> 00:43:23.478
Help me. Oh. God.
Please. please. help me. Help...

316
00:43:25.355 --> 00:43:31.653
Help me. Please. help me.
Help me. Help me. please.

317
00:44:24.665 --> 00:44:26.667
It's happening again.

318
00:46:43.387 --> 00:46:47.766
Help me! Please! Please!

319
00:46:59.987 --> 00:47:02.531
Come on! Come on!

320
00:47:16.670 --> 00:47:18.422
Rose!

321
00:47:20.007 --> 00:47:21.758
Sharon!

322
00:47:25.512 --> 00:47:27.598
Rose!

323
00:48:31.286 --> 00:48:32.871
Rose!

324
00:48:43.799 --> 00:48:45.509
Rose.

325
00:49:00.941 --> 00:49:03.193
- Rose!
- Put your mask on.

326
00:49:03.402 --> 00:49:06.029
Rose. where are you?

327
00:49:12.286 --> 00:49:14.788
- I felt her.
- You what?

328
00:49:14.997 --> 00:49:16.331
Her perfume.

329
00:49:17.708 --> 00:49:19.084
- She was here.
- Who was?

330
00:49:19.293 --> 00:49:21.336
- My wife.
- She wasn't here. Put this mask on.

331
00:49:21.545 --> 00:49:24.298
- Perfume.
- Breathe. Through that mask.

332
00:49:25.799 --> 00:49:28.427
Come on. let's go.
We're gonna go this way.

333
00:49:28.635 --> 00:49:30.429
Chris. come on.

334
00:49:32.431 --> 00:49:34.266
- She was here.
- No. no. she wasn't here.

335
00:49:34.474 --> 00:49:35.434
I know it.

336
00:49:51.241 --> 00:49:52.493
Come on.

337
00:49:52.701 --> 00:49:55.120
Come on. Let's keep looking.

338
00:50:22.064 --> 00:50:24.233
Get off! Get off! Get off!

339
00:50:38.163 --> 00:50:40.040
Get me that pipe.

340
00:50:40.958 --> 00:50:43.168
Rose. the pipe!

341
00:50:44.211 --> 00:50:46.338
Okay. Okay.

342
00:50:48.006 --> 00:50:50.676
- I got it. I got it.
- Quick. come on!

343
00:51:06.108 --> 00:51:07.860
Can we get out of here?

344
00:51:08.443 --> 00:51:10.028
We're trapped.

345
00:51:10.654 --> 00:51:12.114
Last mag.

346
00:51:12.322 --> 00:51:14.992
- That's all the bullets you got?
- Yeah.

347
00:51:17.744 --> 00:51:19.288
Thanks.

348
00:51:31.425 --> 00:51:32.634
You hear that?

349
00:51:40.684 --> 00:51:42.561
That's him.

350
00:51:47.900 --> 00:51:49.860
Stay down! Stay down!

351
00:51:50.068 --> 00:51:52.154
Jesus Christ.

352
00:51:53.780 --> 00:51:55.657
Get down!

353
00:52:02.789 --> 00:52:04.374
Shit!

354
00:53:11.275 --> 00:53:12.276
What?

355
00:53:51.899 --> 00:53:53.233
What the fuck?

356
00:53:54.985 --> 00:53:55.944
What the fuck?

357
00:53:58.280 --> 00:54:00.991
You saw that. right?
That was real?

358
00:54:03.452 --> 00:54:04.870
What the fuck is going on?

359
00:54:05.078 --> 00:54:07.789
All right. I know this is crazy. I know.

360
00:54:07.998 --> 00:54:10.375
We gotta calm right down.
because my kid is not here...

361
00:54:10.584 --> 00:54:13.504
...and I've gotta find her
before this happens again.

362
00:54:14.296 --> 00:54:16.381
I don't even know where to start.

363
00:54:16.798 --> 00:54:18.467
I found this.

364
00:54:18.675 --> 00:54:20.636
It's from a hotel.

365
00:54:20.844 --> 00:54:23.764
I don't know where it is.
but she is in this hotel.

366
00:54:24.556 --> 00:54:26.225
Hotel?

367
00:54:29.645 --> 00:54:31.146
Hey.

368
00:54:32.981 --> 00:54:35.025
It's gonna be okay.

369
00:54:36.777 --> 00:54:38.779
We're gonna be okay.

370
00:54:51.792 --> 00:54:53.627
Now. don't be trying
anything. all right?

371
00:54:53.836 --> 00:54:55.838
We got men up here
all night long.

372
00:54:56.046 --> 00:54:58.757
We're gonna find your wife.
we're gonna find your daughter.

373
00:54:58.966 --> 00:55:01.885
Can't have civilians
wandering around on their own.

374
00:55:02.553 --> 00:55:04.680
You're not telling me everything.

375
00:55:05.973 --> 00:55:07.266
What really happened up here?

376
00:55:07.474 --> 00:55:09.768
Just let it rest in peace.

377
00:55:13.021 --> 00:55:15.440
<i>- Directory assistance.
- Toluca County Archives. please.</i>

378
00:55:15.607 --> 00:55:17.109
<i>One moment.</i>

379
00:55:17.442 --> 00:55:19.778
<i>- Archives?
- Yeah. listen.</i>

380
00:55:19.987 --> 00:55:22.573
Do you have the records there
from Silent Hill?

381
00:55:22.823 --> 00:55:25.909
<i>- Which records. sir?
- The police records.</i>

382
00:55:26.160 --> 00:55:28.579
<i>Sorry. sir.
those records are confidential.</i>

383
00:55:28.787 --> 00:55:30.956
No. no. I can't...
No. listen. I...

384
00:55:31.165 --> 00:55:33.333
<i>Sorry. sir.
I can't access that information.</i>

385
00:55:33.542 --> 00:55:35.002
<i>- Listen. goddamn it.
- Sir.</i>

386
00:55:35.210 --> 00:55:36.628
<i>- This is an emergency.
- I can't...</i>

387
00:55:36.837 --> 00:55:38.797
<i>I can't help you.</i>

388
00:55:55.063 --> 00:55:57.774
They used to say
this place was haunted.

389
00:55:58.400 --> 00:56:00.486
I think they were right.

390
00:56:09.953 --> 00:56:12.539
<i>Help! No!</i>

391
00:56:12.748 --> 00:56:14.583
<i>- Stay away.
- Come on.</i>

392
00:56:14.791 --> 00:56:17.669
Stay away. sinner.

393
00:56:17.878 --> 00:56:19.213
Get back!

394
00:56:19.421 --> 00:56:21.215
Hey.

395
00:56:21.423 --> 00:56:23.133
It's here.

396
00:56:24.968 --> 00:56:27.179
Faith is our destroyer.
Faith has brought us doom.

397
00:56:27.346 --> 00:56:29.223
- Get back!
- Hey. hey!

398
00:56:29.431 --> 00:56:32.351
- Get back!
- Hey. stop.

399
00:56:32.559 --> 00:56:34.937
Think you of thee
who cast the first stone.

400
00:56:35.145 --> 00:56:37.481
Lambs without a shepherd.
shepherd without a flock.

401
00:56:38.190 --> 00:56:40.234
It's your sins which hold you here.

402
00:56:40.442 --> 00:56:41.985
- Stop your lies!
- Calm down.

403
00:56:42.236 --> 00:56:43.195
Calm down. it's okay.

404
00:56:43.362 --> 00:56:45.489
- We're not gonna hurt you.
- She's gone.

405
00:56:46.490 --> 00:56:48.033
What's your name?

406
00:56:48.408 --> 00:56:51.995
Anna. My name is Anna.

407
00:56:52.204 --> 00:56:54.206
What's going on here. Anna?
Who was that?

408
00:56:54.414 --> 00:56:57.501
- I've seen her before.
- Dahlia was cast out.

409
00:56:57.709 --> 00:56:59.753
Not even the darkness wants her.

410
00:56:59.962 --> 00:57:02.548
- She's lost her daughter too.
- What?

411
00:57:02.756 --> 00:57:08.095
- Sinners deserve to lose their spawn.
- What are you doing here. Anna?

412
00:57:09.888 --> 00:57:12.432
Mother needs more food.

413
00:57:13.100 --> 00:57:14.643
You mean there are
other people here?

414
00:57:17.771 --> 00:57:19.731
Christabella keeps us safe.

415
00:57:19.940 --> 00:57:22.359
- Anna.
- We take refuge in the church.

416
00:57:22.901 --> 00:57:25.779
Anna. listen to me.

417
00:57:26.363 --> 00:57:28.740
I've lost my daughter.
She's all alone.

418
00:57:29.116 --> 00:57:31.743
Can you imagine how frightened
she must feel?

419
00:57:31.952 --> 00:57:33.912
Tell me. have you seen her?

420
00:57:34.121 --> 00:57:35.497
Do you know where she is?

421
00:57:39.293 --> 00:57:42.254
If she has faith. she might survive.

422
00:57:42.421 --> 00:57:43.422
If not...

423
00:57:46.425 --> 00:57:47.467
I'm taking this.

424
00:57:49.803 --> 00:57:51.513
Have you seen this?

425
00:57:52.139 --> 00:57:54.349
I've seen it at the school.

426
00:57:54.933 --> 00:57:58.729
It's on all the buildings
the elders of my elders built.

427
00:57:58.937 --> 00:58:03.400
It's a symbol of our unity.
a symbol of our faith.

428
00:58:14.828 --> 00:58:16.497
Rose. look at this.

429
00:58:18.624 --> 00:58:21.752
- What is it?
- Just like yours.

430
00:58:23.170 --> 00:58:26.632
- Where did you find it?
- They're all over the floor.

431
00:58:40.896 --> 00:58:42.105
Rose.

432
00:58:42.856 --> 00:58:44.441
Check this out.

433
00:58:46.318 --> 00:58:50.405
- What number did you take this from?
- 111.

434
00:58:52.407 --> 00:58:54.701
We gotta go to room 111.

435
01:00:28.253 --> 01:00:29.880
Gucci.

436
01:01:00.410 --> 01:01:02.412
<i>- Directory assistance.
- Yeah.</i>

437
01:01:03.080 --> 01:01:05.624
Toluca County Orphanage. please.

438
01:01:05.833 --> 01:01:07.835
<i>One moment. please.</i>

439
01:01:09.753 --> 01:01:12.047
<i>- Yes. I have that information for you.
- Yeah.</i>

440
01:01:13.048 --> 01:01:15.217
Can you give me that address?

441
01:01:24.059 --> 01:01:27.604
We are wandering far
from refuge here.

442
01:01:29.815 --> 01:01:32.734
Let's keep her with us.
She's all we got.

443
01:01:59.970 --> 01:02:01.597
There's no room 111.

444
01:02:01.805 --> 01:02:04.224
The first burning.

445
01:02:05.100 --> 01:02:08.604
- What is it. Anna?
- The first burning.

446
01:02:08.812 --> 01:02:10.731
Before the town had a name.

447
01:02:10.939 --> 01:02:14.401
The elders of my elders
kept us pure.

448
01:02:14.985 --> 01:02:17.321
The founders of this town
were witch-hunters.

449
01:02:17.821 --> 01:02:20.324
Burning the witch
held back the darkness.

450
01:02:20.532 --> 01:02:22.159
It stopped the apocalypse.

451
01:02:28.040 --> 01:02:29.666
It's here.

452
01:02:46.058 --> 01:02:48.227
There's a room in here.

453
01:02:59.655 --> 01:03:01.281
Look at this.

454
01:03:09.248 --> 01:03:10.791
Here.

455
01:03:11.500 --> 01:03:13.210
Damn.

456
01:03:28.308 --> 01:03:30.519
What is this place?

457
01:03:30.727 --> 01:03:32.938
I don't know.
We're in the next building.

458
01:03:33.105 --> 01:03:35.190
Some factory. maybe?

459
01:03:36.942 --> 01:03:39.069
Looks like there was a fire.

460
01:03:45.784 --> 01:03:47.161
Hey.

461
01:04:08.140 --> 01:04:09.808
Rose!

462
01:04:40.631 --> 01:04:42.466
Who are you?

463
01:04:54.895 --> 01:04:56.688
It's okay.

464
01:04:57.898 --> 01:05:01.193
Don't be scared.
I promise I'm not gonna hurt you.

465
01:05:19.545 --> 01:05:21.171
Rose?

466
01:05:43.068 --> 01:05:45.362
Okay. Come on.

467
01:05:45.571 --> 01:05:47.239
Come on.

468
01:05:51.535 --> 01:05:54.621
It's okay. Hey.

469
01:05:54.913 --> 01:05:56.331
Hey.

470
01:05:59.334 --> 01:06:01.003
It's okay.

471
01:06:08.135 --> 01:06:09.428
It's okay.

472
01:06:09.636 --> 01:06:11.805
I'm not gonna hurt you.

473
01:06:22.107 --> 01:06:23.317
Oh. my God.

474
01:06:23.984 --> 01:06:26.069
You could be her twin.

475
01:06:30.282 --> 01:06:32.242
Are you Alessa?

476
01:06:33.994 --> 01:06:36.079
Where's my Sharon?

477
01:06:36.788 --> 01:06:38.624
Look at me.

478
01:06:40.083 --> 01:06:42.044
I'm burning.

479
01:06:44.880 --> 01:06:46.381
Rose?

480
01:06:49.259 --> 01:06:50.344
Rose? My God.

481
01:06:51.303 --> 01:06:53.806
- How did you get over there?
- Where is she?

482
01:06:58.185 --> 01:06:59.561
Grab onto it.

483
01:07:00.979 --> 01:07:04.566
- Now swing back around.
- Okay.

484
01:07:09.363 --> 01:07:10.739
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

485
01:07:11.156 --> 01:07:12.825
What the hell
were you doing over there?

486
01:07:13.033 --> 01:07:14.535
You're gonna get yourself killed.

487
01:07:15.327 --> 01:07:17.412
I think I just saw Dahlia's daughter.

488
01:07:19.122 --> 01:07:20.833
She was the one
that brought us here.

489
01:07:20.999 --> 01:07:22.292
What are you talking about?

490
01:07:22.501 --> 01:07:24.878
She was the one
that made me crash my car.

491
01:07:25.587 --> 01:07:26.797
Alessa.

492
01:07:27.005 --> 01:07:29.174
We don't say her name.

493
01:07:32.970 --> 01:07:35.472
That's the seal. isn't it. Anna?

494
01:07:36.515 --> 01:07:38.851
The symbol of your faith?

495
01:07:41.603 --> 01:07:43.814
Something terrible happened here.

496
01:07:48.026 --> 01:07:51.196
We have to leave.
We have to leave!

497
01:07:52.531 --> 01:07:54.700
- The darkness is coming!
- Let's go.

498
01:07:55.159 --> 01:07:56.743
Let's go!

499
01:08:08.547 --> 01:08:10.799
The church isn't far.

500
01:08:11.008 --> 01:08:12.885
- Run. Run!
- Rose. come on!

501
01:08:13.093 --> 01:08:14.803
Rose!

502
01:08:24.730 --> 01:08:26.356
Hurry!

503
01:08:33.530 --> 01:08:34.740
Rose.

504
01:08:34.907 --> 01:08:37.409
- Come!
- We gotta go.

505
01:08:55.093 --> 01:08:57.012
- Rose. come on.
- I've seen this.

506
01:09:08.649 --> 01:09:10.359
Rose. let's go!

507
01:09:12.444 --> 01:09:15.072
- Cybil!
- Rose. come on.

508
01:09:23.038 --> 01:09:23.997
Cybil!

509
01:09:24.206 --> 01:09:27.084
You run not towards sanctuary
but from your fears.

510
01:09:27.292 --> 01:09:30.003
Do not join the others.
They are deceivers. They are damned.

511
01:09:30.212 --> 01:09:31.755
- We gotta get inside.
- No!

512
01:09:31.964 --> 01:09:33.549
They are wolves
in the skin of sheep.

513
01:09:33.757 --> 01:09:36.593
They brought about their own hell.
They'll take you with them.

514
01:09:36.802 --> 01:09:39.012
- Filth and lies!
- Hey!

515
01:09:39.221 --> 01:09:40.639
Stop it!

516
01:09:41.974 --> 01:09:45.102
Please. I've seen your daughter.
I've seen Alessa.

517
01:09:48.105 --> 01:09:50.691
- It's coming!
- She's dead. isn't she?

518
01:09:50.899 --> 01:09:52.568
Fire doesn't cleanse. it blackens.

519
01:09:53.068 --> 01:09:55.070
- Listen to me.
- Rose. hurry!

520
01:09:55.445 --> 01:09:57.489
She looks exactly like Sharon.

521
01:09:57.698 --> 01:10:00.159
She brought us here. didn't she?

522
01:10:03.871 --> 01:10:06.081
Why? What does she want?

523
01:10:06.290 --> 01:10:07.958
Evil wakes in vengeance.

524
01:10:08.167 --> 01:10:10.794
Be careful what you choose.

525
01:10:30.731 --> 01:10:32.232
Rose!

526
01:11:06.350 --> 01:11:07.726
Oh. God. no.

527
01:11:29.748 --> 01:11:31.083
- Witches!
- She's evil.

528
01:11:31.291 --> 01:11:32.501
Keep away the witches!

529
01:11:36.088 --> 01:11:38.048
- No.
- Send them back!

530
01:11:38.674 --> 01:11:40.092
No.

531
01:11:40.634 --> 01:11:42.094
We're lost.

532
01:11:52.396 --> 01:11:53.856
This is a sanctuary.

533
01:12:03.949 --> 01:12:07.411
Please. Christabella.
they lured my Anna.

534
01:12:07.619 --> 01:12:10.038
They gave her to the fiend.

535
01:12:10.372 --> 01:12:13.959
Eleanor. you must remember
that Anna went against our laws.

536
01:12:14.168 --> 01:12:16.879
She went alone outside
into the devil's playground.

537
01:12:19.089 --> 01:12:22.384
She was not the responsibility
of these two strangers.

538
01:12:24.344 --> 01:12:26.472
We'll deal with them later.

539
01:12:32.436 --> 01:12:34.438
Now we must pray.

540
01:12:55.375 --> 01:12:56.585
And then I saw them...

541
01:12:56.793 --> 01:13:00.172
...from whose presence
earth and heaven fled away.

542
01:13:00.631 --> 01:13:03.217
And no home was left to them.

543
01:13:03.425 --> 01:13:05.511
And then I saw them...

544
01:13:05.719 --> 01:13:09.014
...from whose presence
earth and heaven fled away.

545
01:13:09.181 --> 01:13:11.892
And no home was left to them.

546
01:13:12.351 --> 01:13:15.103
And I saw the dead.
the great and the small...

547
01:13:15.312 --> 01:13:18.482
...and they were judged
according to their deeds.

548
01:13:18.690 --> 01:13:23.695
And I saw the dead.
the great and the small...

549
01:13:23.904 --> 01:13:27.115
...and they were judged
according to their deeds.

550
01:13:29.660 --> 01:13:34.039
And anyone's name not found
written in the book of life...

551
01:13:34.206 --> 01:13:37.376
...they will be thrown
into the lake of fire.

552
01:13:47.886 --> 01:13:50.722
And now I lay me down to sleep...

553
01:13:50.931 --> 01:13:53.851
...I pray the Lord my soul to keep.

554
01:13:54.059 --> 01:13:56.520
If I should die before I wake...

555
01:13:57.062 --> 01:14:00.274
...I pray the Lord my soul to take.

556
01:14:00.482 --> 01:14:02.317
Amen.

557
01:14:02.734 --> 01:14:05.445
All right. girls. into bed.
Quickly. now.

558
01:14:05.654 --> 01:14:08.240
No better place to be
on a rainy night.

559
01:14:08.448 --> 01:14:11.827
In you go. Lindsey. thattagirl.
You've got your bear. that's a girl.

560
01:14:12.035 --> 01:14:14.413
No. No talking
after lights are out.

561
01:14:18.208 --> 01:14:20.127
Good night. children.

562
01:14:20.335 --> 01:14:22.337
And God bless.

563
01:14:26.341 --> 01:14:28.844
I'm sorry. Sister Margaret.
this really can't wait.

564
01:14:29.761 --> 01:14:31.555
I can't imagine why.

565
01:14:33.474 --> 01:14:35.267
Nine years ago...

566
01:14:35.476 --> 01:14:37.478
...a baby was left
outside this orphanage.

567
01:14:37.686 --> 01:14:39.771
My wife and I were the ones
who adopted her.

568
01:14:39.980 --> 01:14:42.774
I'm very happy for you.
Mr. Da Silva...

569
01:14:42.983 --> 01:14:46.778
...but I can't give out
information on our children.

570
01:14:48.405 --> 01:14:49.698
Look.

571
01:14:51.074 --> 01:14:54.077
That girl. she looks
exactly like my daughter.

572
01:14:54.286 --> 01:14:56.246
I can't help you. I'm sorry.

573
01:14:56.455 --> 01:14:59.082
- It's late.
- She must be 40 now.

574
01:14:59.291 --> 01:15:00.501
Where can I find her?

575
01:15:01.376 --> 01:15:03.295
This story isn't hers alone...

576
01:15:03.462 --> 01:15:05.172
...but all of ours!
- You people.

577
01:15:05.380 --> 01:15:06.548
You got yourself something.

578
01:15:06.757 --> 01:15:09.718
You know what you got now. Chris?
How about breaking and entering?

579
01:15:09.927 --> 01:15:12.012
By the looks of this.
a little assault as well.

580
01:15:12.721 --> 01:15:14.431
Thank you. Thomas.

581
01:15:14.640 --> 01:15:17.267
- This can't go any farther.
- It won't. Sister.

582
01:15:18.769 --> 01:15:20.938
You know.
I have some 12-year-olds...

583
01:15:21.146 --> 01:15:23.482
...who cover their tracks
better than you do.

584
01:15:23.899 --> 01:15:25.192
What's this?

585
01:15:25.400 --> 01:15:26.944
Look. Gucci. do you know her?

586
01:15:27.152 --> 01:15:29.613
Is that my daughter's birth mother?

587
01:15:34.827 --> 01:15:38.288
- Look. turn around.
- What are you doing?

588
01:15:40.374 --> 01:15:43.418
I knew that girl. I did.

589
01:15:44.586 --> 01:15:47.130
I was told she didn't make it
through the night.

590
01:15:47.589 --> 01:15:49.508
The night of the fire.

591
01:15:49.800 --> 01:15:51.802
The night of the big fire
in Silent Hill.

592
01:15:54.138 --> 01:15:56.515
There were these people...

593
01:15:58.517 --> 01:15:59.685
...these fanatics.

594
01:15:59.893 --> 01:16:03.147
What they did
to that child was terrible.

595
01:16:03.355 --> 01:16:06.066
That was 30 years ago.
and it's over now.

596
01:16:06.525 --> 01:16:08.152
Not as far as I'm concerned.

597
01:16:08.819 --> 01:16:10.821
What's it gonna be. city boy?

598
01:16:11.029 --> 01:16:13.532
I can put you in jail...

599
01:16:13.740 --> 01:16:15.409
...or you can go home.

600
01:16:16.034 --> 01:16:18.745
And that's your definition of justice?

601
01:16:19.913 --> 01:16:23.667
Many different forms
of justice. Chris.

602
01:16:24.376 --> 01:16:27.421
See. you've got man's. God's...

603
01:16:28.422 --> 01:16:30.340
...and even the devil's.

604
01:16:31.758 --> 01:16:34.511
Certain forms you just can't control.

605
01:16:35.471 --> 01:16:37.681
So I want you to go home now...

606
01:16:38.056 --> 01:16:40.309
...to your nice warm bed...

607
01:16:40.517 --> 01:16:42.936
...and let me deal with this town...

608
01:16:43.145 --> 01:16:45.898
...and what has happened
over the last 30 years.

609
01:16:46.064 --> 01:16:48.859
Okay? End of story.

610
01:17:01.246 --> 01:17:03.665
Tell me first how you got here.

611
01:17:05.792 --> 01:17:08.253
Honestly. I don't know
how I got here.

612
01:17:08.462 --> 01:17:11.340
Right now. I've lost my little girl...

613
01:17:11.548 --> 01:17:14.176
...and all I know is that
I'm supposed to be in this church.

614
01:17:14.384 --> 01:17:16.386
Are you a person of faith?

615
01:17:16.595 --> 01:17:18.889
- I love my daughter.
- That's not what I asked.

616
01:17:19.264 --> 01:17:20.390
Who are you to judge?

617
01:17:20.599 --> 01:17:23.811
We judge because the souls of history
hang in the balance.

618
01:17:24.019 --> 01:17:25.646
Because our faith
has never failed us.

619
01:17:25.854 --> 01:17:28.273
Our faith keeps the darkness
of hell at bay.

620
01:17:28.482 --> 01:17:32.069
Then use your faith
to help me find my little girl.

621
01:17:32.736 --> 01:17:34.738
Only the demon knows where she is.

622
01:17:34.947 --> 01:17:37.199
Then tell me.
where do I find this demon?

623
01:17:39.076 --> 01:17:41.578
No one has ever returned
from the core of the darkness...

624
01:17:41.787 --> 01:17:43.163
...where the demon lies in wait.

625
01:17:43.372 --> 01:17:44.790
She's not gonna help us.
Let's go.

626
01:17:44.998 --> 01:17:47.543
If you wish to face the demon
to find your daughter...

627
01:17:47.751 --> 01:17:48.961
...I won't stop you.

628
01:17:49.127 --> 01:17:51.797
- Christabella. they can't go down...
- Silence. Adam.

629
01:17:55.551 --> 01:17:58.220
Perhaps your faith will protect you.

630
01:17:58.679 --> 01:18:00.764
Perhaps not.

631
01:18:14.611 --> 01:18:16.822
If you don't wanna do this...

632
01:18:17.823 --> 01:18:19.825
...I'll understand.

633
01:18:21.034 --> 01:18:22.995
Sharon's adopted...

634
01:18:23.912 --> 01:18:25.164
...but I'm her mother.

635
01:18:25.330 --> 01:18:28.417
I knew that from the moment
I first laid eyes on her.

636
01:18:30.752 --> 01:18:32.671
She's lucky to have you.

637
01:18:34.089 --> 01:18:36.800
Mother is God in the eyes of a child.

638
01:19:47.704 --> 01:19:49.122
Quiet.

639
01:19:49.414 --> 01:19:51.959
We're in his domain now.

640
01:19:57.422 --> 01:19:59.716
Look at this map. Memorize it.

641
01:20:00.759 --> 01:20:02.886
Your memory may save your life.

642
01:20:04.263 --> 01:20:07.224
- Do you see this room?
- Yeah.

643
01:20:07.432 --> 01:20:10.102
That is where the darkness lies.

644
01:20:10.310 --> 01:20:12.729
The demon is in the bowels
of this building.

645
01:20:12.938 --> 01:20:15.274
It hides behind the face
of an innocent.

646
01:20:15.482 --> 01:20:16.775
You mean a child?

647
01:20:16.984 --> 01:20:19.278
Don't believe your eyes.
Your eyes will lie to you.

648
01:20:19.444 --> 01:20:22.531
Faith is the only truth.

649
01:20:23.615 --> 01:20:24.783
I will pray for you. Rose...

650
01:20:24.992 --> 01:20:28.287
...but I won't expect you
and your friend to return.

651
01:20:29.121 --> 01:20:30.664
Goodbye.

652
01:20:33.125 --> 01:20:34.459
Adam.

653
01:20:35.669 --> 01:20:38.172
Left. Right.

654
01:20:38.881 --> 01:20:41.216
Left. Left.

655
01:20:42.468 --> 01:20:46.346
- Right. Right. Left.
- Take them to the lower level.

656
01:20:46.555 --> 01:20:48.348
- In the basement?
- Do it. then return.

657
01:20:48.557 --> 01:20:50.934
- Left. 3A.
- But...

658
01:20:51.143 --> 01:20:52.686
- Right. 4A.
- I said. do it.

659
01:20:53.520 --> 01:20:57.024
- Left. Left. Right.
- Rose. Rose.

660
01:20:57.608 --> 01:21:02.112
- Left. Right. Left. Left.
- Rose. she's killing you.

661
01:21:02.321 --> 01:21:04.615
- Rose!
- Let me do this.

662
01:21:05.616 --> 01:21:07.784
I need to do this.

663
01:21:25.803 --> 01:21:27.346
Take this.

664
01:21:27.554 --> 01:21:31.391
They'll be drawn to the light.
but you won't be able to see without it.

665
01:21:34.228 --> 01:21:35.938
Thank you.

666
01:21:42.361 --> 01:21:45.113
- So this thing actually works?
- It will.

667
01:21:45.322 --> 01:21:47.324
If the demon wants you. it will.

668
01:21:49.535 --> 01:21:50.702
Forgive me.

669
01:21:52.120 --> 01:21:54.790
We've lived too long as scavengers.
I believe this is yours.

670
01:22:02.422 --> 01:22:05.134
Witch! Her child's
the likeness of Alessa.

671
01:22:05.342 --> 01:22:06.677
Her child's the next vessel.

672
01:22:06.885 --> 01:22:09.680
Stop her!
Don't let the witches go down!

673
01:22:14.560 --> 01:22:16.061
Come on!

674
01:22:25.654 --> 01:22:26.947
Get off her!

675
01:22:29.158 --> 01:22:30.450
Find her.

676
01:22:31.201 --> 01:22:33.871
No! Wait! Cybil!

677
01:22:34.079 --> 01:22:36.206
Cybil! Open the door!

678
01:22:59.062 --> 01:23:01.690
No!

679
01:24:30.362 --> 01:24:31.947
8A.

680
01:24:32.489 --> 01:24:36.785
7 A. Right.

681
01:24:46.879 --> 01:24:50.090
Right. 6A.

682
01:24:51.550 --> 01:24:53.469
4A.

683
01:24:54.511 --> 01:24:56.346
3A.

684
01:24:58.974 --> 01:25:01.727
Left. left. Right. right.

685
01:25:01.894 --> 01:25:04.563
Left. left.

686
01:26:18.637 --> 01:26:22.558
Okay. I can do this.

687
01:27:33.629 --> 01:27:36.548
<i>Congratulations. Rose.</i>

688
01:27:36.715 --> 01:27:38.342
<i>You're here.</i>

689
01:27:39.968 --> 01:27:41.512
<i>You did it.</i>

690
01:27:43.263 --> 01:27:47.643
<i>Your reward is the truth.</i>

691
01:27:50.395 --> 01:27:54.483
<i>Did you see that Alessa
was a good little girl?</i>

692
01:27:57.194 --> 01:28:00.697
<i>Even though nobody
looked at her that way.</i>

693
01:28:01.448 --> 01:28:06.912
<i>- Burn the witch! Burn the witch!
- Their parents told them she was bad.</i>

694
01:28:07.955 --> 01:28:11.291
<i>She didn't have a father
like they did.</i>

695
01:28:17.589 --> 01:28:20.551
<i>Alessa was alone in the world.</i>

696
01:28:24.930 --> 01:28:29.351
<i>You know what can happen
to little girls when they're left alone.</i>

697
01:28:33.397 --> 01:28:35.399
It's okay. it's me. come on.

698
01:28:35.607 --> 01:28:37.985
<i>Even her mother couldn't help.</i>

699
01:28:40.404 --> 01:28:43.365
<i>Even though she loved her baby.</i>

700
01:28:44.283 --> 01:28:47.161
<i>But the rest of the family
didn't love Alessa.</i>

701
01:28:47.369 --> 01:28:50.622
<i>They were just like the others
and made her scared.</i>

702
01:28:50.831 --> 01:28:52.708
We know.
Even the children know it.

703
01:28:52.916 --> 01:28:54.418
Your daughter...

704
01:28:55.752 --> 01:28:58.046
Why you won't
just name the father...

705
01:29:01.508 --> 01:29:04.178
You've brought sin amongst us.

706
01:29:04.386 --> 01:29:06.305
The faithful must gather
in judgment...

707
01:29:06.513 --> 01:29:09.600
...for we are called to purify this filth.

708
01:29:09.850 --> 01:29:11.685
What does she mean. Mommy?

709
01:29:12.269 --> 01:29:15.564
You're weak. my dear sister.
You always were.

710
01:29:15.772 --> 01:29:19.276
Trust us. Dahlia.
Have faith in our virtue.

711
01:29:19.485 --> 01:29:21.945
We will restore innocence.

712
01:29:22.654 --> 01:29:26.825
<i>They had met many times
since the town was built...</i>

713
01:29:27.034 --> 01:29:30.245
<i>... to restore innocence and purity.</i>

714
01:29:31.246 --> 01:29:33.457
<i>They had a special place for that.</i>

715
01:29:45.969 --> 01:29:48.388
<i>Do you remember the hotel?</i>

716
01:29:48.972 --> 01:29:51.725
<i>I led you to all these places...</i>

717
01:29:51.934 --> 01:29:55.354
<i>... and you were very good
at following my clues.</i>

718
01:29:56.188 --> 01:29:58.357
You may leave. Dahlia.

719
01:29:59.149 --> 01:30:00.984
We fight the sin. not the sinner.

720
01:30:01.568 --> 01:30:03.779
Mommy! Mommy!

721
01:30:04.530 --> 01:30:06.031
Mommy!

722
01:30:06.240 --> 01:30:09.535
<i>You know how that feels.
don't you. Rose?</i>

723
01:30:10.118 --> 01:30:12.454
<i>To lose your little girl?</i>

724
01:30:13.205 --> 01:30:15.332
What have I done?

725
01:30:17.876 --> 01:30:22.131
- Oh. God.
- Weep not for the demon.

726
01:30:22.714 --> 01:30:23.924
No!

727
01:30:24.133 --> 01:30:27.886
Once again
we are locked in mortal battle.

728
01:30:28.554 --> 01:30:32.099
<i>They thought they knew
how to cast out evil.</i>

729
01:30:33.267 --> 01:30:37.062
- Praise God for our clarity.
- Amen.

730
01:30:37.229 --> 01:30:41.441
Praise the innocent
for their sacrifice.

731
01:30:41.650 --> 01:30:43.610
<i>But you should be careful
how you fight evil.</i>

732
01:30:43.819 --> 01:30:46.905
- They give us back our purity.
- Purity.

733
01:30:50.075 --> 01:30:51.994
- And our unity.
- Unity.

734
01:30:52.202 --> 01:30:55.831
<i>Your weapons
can turn back on you.</i>

735
01:31:21.315 --> 01:31:22.649
No.

736
01:31:24.443 --> 01:31:25.777
No.

737
01:31:25.944 --> 01:31:29.031
<i>Now you know
why Dahlia is broken.</i>

738
01:31:30.657 --> 01:31:33.035
<i>She tried to get help...</i>

739
01:31:33.243 --> 01:31:35.370
<i>... but she went too late.</i>

740
01:31:36.788 --> 01:31:38.957
Get her up. boys.
Get her up now!

741
01:31:39.333 --> 01:31:41.627
<i>There were good people
in the town...</i>

742
01:31:41.793 --> 01:31:44.046
<i>... people like you. Rose.</i>

743
01:31:44.254 --> 01:31:46.673
<i>People who like to help.</i>

744
01:31:49.426 --> 01:31:53.764
<i>Alessa was so lonely
and hurt and scared.</i>

745
01:31:54.306 --> 01:31:57.017
<i>They should have known better
than to hurt her so badly.</i>

746
01:32:00.437 --> 01:32:03.023
<i>When you're hurt
and scared for so long...</i>

747
01:32:03.982 --> 01:32:06.443
<i>... your fear and pain turn to hate...</i>

748
01:32:06.652 --> 01:32:10.697
<i>... and the hate
starts to change the world.</i>

749
01:32:13.534 --> 01:32:18.455
<i>Alessa's hate grew and grew.
burning inside her.</i>

750
01:32:22.751 --> 01:32:25.420
<i>Her hate got so strong...</i>

751
01:32:26.004 --> 01:32:29.758
<i>... she even hurt someone
who was only curious.</i>

752
01:32:44.106 --> 01:32:46.275
<i>That's when I came.</i>

753
01:32:53.365 --> 01:32:55.325
<i>I told her it was their turn.</i>

754
01:32:57.244 --> 01:33:02.958
<i>I promised they would all
fall into her darkest dream.</i>

755
01:33:32.654 --> 01:33:37.326
<i>Now. Rose. we must talk.</i>

756
01:34:30.045 --> 01:34:32.422
Don't be afraid.

757
01:34:38.679 --> 01:34:40.597
She won't hurt you.

758
01:34:41.223 --> 01:34:43.433
She needs your help.

759
01:34:43.642 --> 01:34:44.810
Who is she?

760
01:34:45.894 --> 01:34:48.981
- She is Alessa.
- Then who are you?

761
01:34:49.439 --> 01:34:53.360
I have many names.

762
01:34:53.944 --> 01:34:57.739
Right now.
I'm the dark part of Alessa.

763
01:34:59.158 --> 01:35:00.576
Where's my child?

764
01:35:01.076 --> 01:35:04.079
She's not your child.

765
01:35:06.165 --> 01:35:07.457
She's hers.

766
01:35:08.542 --> 01:35:12.254
The little girl is
what's left of her goodness.

767
01:35:12.588 --> 01:35:14.173
We hid her in safety...

768
01:35:15.257 --> 01:35:17.509
...in the world outside this hell.

769
01:35:30.439 --> 01:35:34.735
Now the dream
of this life must end...

770
01:35:34.943 --> 01:35:38.822
...and so. too.
must the dreamers within it.

771
01:35:39.031 --> 01:35:41.366
For over 30 years...

772
01:35:41.533 --> 01:35:44.661
...they've lied to their own souls.

773
01:35:44.870 --> 01:35:49.082
For 30 years they've denied
their own fate.

774
01:35:49.291 --> 01:35:52.419
But now is the end of days...

775
01:35:52.628 --> 01:35:55.464
...and I am the reaper.

776
01:35:55.964 --> 01:35:57.633
What do you want?

777
01:35:57.966 --> 01:36:00.344
All we ask for is satisfaction.

778
01:36:00.969 --> 01:36:02.346
Satisfaction?

779
01:36:03.222 --> 01:36:05.140
Revenge.

780
01:36:06.975 --> 01:36:08.685
Why me?

781
01:36:09.144 --> 01:36:11.063
You chose.

782
01:36:11.563 --> 01:36:13.857
You chose Sharon.

783
01:36:14.066 --> 01:36:17.319
Christabella will find Sharon.

784
01:36:17.528 --> 01:36:20.405
She plans to purify her.

785
01:36:22.658 --> 01:36:24.660
Oh. God. no.

786
01:36:25.285 --> 01:36:28.664
Their blind conviction
repels me from their church.

787
01:36:29.456 --> 01:36:32.543
I cannot enter
while they deny their fate...

788
01:36:32.751 --> 01:36:34.211
...but you can.

789
01:36:35.087 --> 01:36:39.883
- Just tell me what I need to do.
- Tell them the truth.

790
01:37:52.748 --> 01:37:54.666
The child is mine!

791
01:37:54.833 --> 01:37:56.835
Mine!

792
01:38:02.341 --> 01:38:04.218
She's mine.

793
01:38:06.011 --> 01:38:07.888
She's mine!

794
01:38:13.894 --> 01:38:17.147
The truth is clear to those who see.

795
01:38:18.232 --> 01:38:21.819
Just as I could see
you had this child.

796
01:38:40.671 --> 01:38:42.172
Let's go.

797
01:38:44.883 --> 01:38:47.970
Out of the car. Turn around.

798
01:39:03.026 --> 01:39:04.987
Just a friendly warning...

799
01:39:05.571 --> 01:39:08.031
...I'll be back with people
who know what they're doing.

800
01:39:10.868 --> 01:39:14.580
Before you do that. Chris.
I wanna tell you about Officer Bennett.

801
01:39:16.248 --> 01:39:19.209
Few years back. some wacko.
he abducted a kid...

802
01:39:19.418 --> 01:39:22.546
...threw him down a mine vent
up there in Silent Hill.

803
01:39:22.963 --> 01:39:25.257
Cybil Bennett. she found that boy.

804
01:39:25.424 --> 01:39:27.134
She spent three days
holding onto him...

805
01:39:27.342 --> 01:39:29.553
...keeping him alive
until they were rescued.

806
01:39:29.761 --> 01:39:31.180
We know what we're doing.

807
01:39:31.388 --> 01:39:33.348
I need to do everything I can.

808
01:39:40.314 --> 01:39:42.107
Let's go.

809
01:40:05.798 --> 01:40:08.008
Please.
Christabella. let her live.

810
01:40:08.217 --> 01:40:10.469
Your weakness
led these souls to judgment.

811
01:40:10.636 --> 01:40:12.930
- This time you will bear witness.
- She is innocent.

812
01:40:13.138 --> 01:40:16.099
Look at her.
She's the whelp of your daughter.

813
01:40:16.308 --> 01:40:17.518
The demon!

814
01:40:18.101 --> 01:40:23.315
The demon fathered this disgusting
abomination from her child!

815
01:40:23.524 --> 01:40:24.566
No. she's mine!

816
01:40:27.736 --> 01:40:29.780
Sharon. Sharon. look at me.

817
01:40:29.988 --> 01:40:32.574
Look at me. Don't be afraid.

818
01:40:32.783 --> 01:40:36.286
It's okay. it's okay.
Your mama's coming.

819
01:40:37.037 --> 01:40:40.707
Once again we are called upon
to restore innocence.

820
01:40:40.916 --> 01:40:44.795
We burn this witch.
We vanquish evil.

821
01:40:45.712 --> 01:40:47.881
No. You can't. You can't.

822
01:40:48.090 --> 01:40:50.717
- Don't let her say this! No!
- We burn the child!

823
01:40:50.926 --> 01:40:53.137
We fight the demon!

824
01:40:56.140 --> 01:40:57.391
She's just a child!

825
01:40:57.599 --> 01:41:00.519
What the fuck is wrong
with you people?

826
01:41:01.019 --> 01:41:02.938
Let her go!

827
01:41:03.397 --> 01:41:05.607
Leave her alone!

828
01:41:05.816 --> 01:41:07.442
Leave her alone!

829
01:41:08.152 --> 01:41:10.028
Those who aid the demon...

830
01:41:10.195 --> 01:41:14.032
...they must be cleansed
by the fire from whence they came.

831
01:41:14.199 --> 01:41:16.785
That's crazy. You're crazy.

832
01:41:17.536 --> 01:41:19.705
No!

833
01:41:19.913 --> 01:41:21.540
Why are you listening to this?

834
01:41:21.748 --> 01:41:24.042
Why?

835
01:41:25.878 --> 01:41:28.839
<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>

836
01:41:29.047 --> 01:41:34.136
<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!
Burn the witch!</i>

837
01:41:41.185 --> 01:41:42.978
Sharon.

838
01:41:50.235 --> 01:41:52.237
Evil witch!

839
01:41:53.197 --> 01:41:55.199
Suffer.

840
01:41:59.620 --> 01:42:02.247
<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>

841
01:42:02.456 --> 01:42:06.251
<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>

842
01:42:11.632 --> 01:42:14.009
Oh. my God.

843
01:42:21.266 --> 01:42:26.396
<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!
Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>

844
01:42:26.605 --> 01:42:31.693
<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!
Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>

845
01:42:31.902 --> 01:42:33.445
Burn her!

846
01:42:35.864 --> 01:42:38.200
You're in your own hell.

847
01:42:46.375 --> 01:42:50.087
Mama. be with me.

848
01:43:13.485 --> 01:43:15.362
Here is where the apocalypse began.

849
01:43:15.571 --> 01:43:18.407
This is where we stopped
the annihilation of the world.

850
01:43:18.615 --> 01:43:21.118
We drew a line in the sand
and said:

851
01:43:21.326 --> 01:43:23.745
"Demon. you will not cross!"

852
01:43:23.954 --> 01:43:27.624
But the demon is wicked.
full of treachery.

853
01:43:27.833 --> 01:43:31.962
Yet again he comes to tempt us
in the guise of an innocent.

854
01:43:32.171 --> 01:43:34.173
To rid the world of this demon...

855
01:43:34.381 --> 01:43:37.009
...we must burn this child!

856
01:43:38.844 --> 01:43:40.846
That's not gonna happen!

857
01:43:43.891 --> 01:43:44.850
Mommy!

858
01:43:45.976 --> 01:43:49.354
It's okay. baby.
Everything's gonna be okay.

859
01:43:49.563 --> 01:43:51.315
Oh. my God.

860
01:43:51.523 --> 01:43:53.567
Oh. my God.

861
01:43:53.775 --> 01:43:55.903
What have you people done?

862
01:43:56.111 --> 01:43:59.364
- You have returned.
- Yes. I have.

863
01:44:00.032 --> 01:44:01.992
The witch has returned.

864
01:44:04.995 --> 01:44:08.624
Do not believe her lies.

865
01:44:09.041 --> 01:44:11.043
I come from a world
outside this place.

866
01:44:11.502 --> 01:44:13.253
I come from a world full of life!

867
01:44:16.757 --> 01:44:18.258
Why don't you tell them the truth.

868
01:44:18.467 --> 01:44:21.887
Tell them the truth that you deny.
even to yourself.

869
01:44:22.095 --> 01:44:24.264
There was no apocalypse!

870
01:44:24.473 --> 01:44:26.517
You burned in the fire
that you started...

871
01:44:26.725 --> 01:44:30.020
...and nothing can save you
because you're already damned!

872
01:44:31.897 --> 01:44:33.190
- Mommy!
- Take her.

873
01:44:33.565 --> 01:44:35.943
Burn her. Burn her as a witch.

874
01:44:36.568 --> 01:44:39.196
Burn her! Burn her!

875
01:44:39.571 --> 01:44:40.906
Demon witch!

876
01:44:41.073 --> 01:44:42.658
- Burn me?
- Demon witch.

877
01:44:42.866 --> 01:44:44.785
That's your answer.

878
01:44:45.369 --> 01:44:47.329
Burn anything you're afraid of.

879
01:44:47.538 --> 01:44:50.040
Burn anything you can't control.

880
01:44:51.959 --> 01:44:55.420
This woman uses your fear
to control you.

881
01:44:55.587 --> 01:44:58.132
She led you to burn
Alessa Gillespie.

882
01:44:58.340 --> 01:45:01.176
She led you to burn
an innocent child.

883
01:45:01.385 --> 01:45:04.555
But you will not deny your guilt...

884
01:45:04.763 --> 01:45:07.307
...and you cannot deny her pain!

885
01:45:07.516 --> 01:45:10.686
That child was sin incarnate.

886
01:45:11.186 --> 01:45:14.731
No. it's you who have sinned.

887
01:45:15.983 --> 01:45:19.027
You darkened the heart
of an innocent...

888
01:45:19.236 --> 01:45:23.115
...and now you cower in the face
of Alessa's revenge.

889
01:45:23.282 --> 01:45:25.284
- Sinner.
- Heresy.

890
01:45:25.450 --> 01:45:27.494
Burn her. Burn her!

891
01:45:28.829 --> 01:45:32.875
Your faith brings death!

892
01:45:34.251 --> 01:45:36.170
You are alone in this limbo...

893
01:45:36.378 --> 01:45:39.131
...and God is not here.

894
01:45:40.549 --> 01:45:41.592
Mommy!

895
01:45:54.980 --> 01:45:59.026
She was a blasphemer.

896
01:45:59.860 --> 01:46:02.321
Blasphemer!

897
01:46:05.282 --> 01:46:07.117
Blasphemer!

898
01:47:22.693 --> 01:47:24.444
What have you done?

899
01:47:25.362 --> 01:47:27.281
You've brought the darkness in
with you.

900
01:47:28.365 --> 01:47:30.409
Do you know what you've done?

901
01:47:39.585 --> 01:47:41.462
For Sharon.

902
01:47:46.175 --> 01:47:47.885
Mommy.

903
01:47:48.093 --> 01:47:50.929
Mommy. Mommy.

904
01:49:04.461 --> 01:49:06.046
Mommy!

905
01:49:34.992 --> 01:49:38.912
Oh. Lord. give me the strength
to stay pure.

906
01:50:13.197 --> 01:50:15.699
No! No!

907
01:50:47.731 --> 01:50:51.860
Alessa. what have you become?

908
01:51:05.958 --> 01:51:07.835
Mommy!

909
01:51:09.086 --> 01:51:12.506
Sharon! Sharon. honey. it's me.
It's Mommy.

910
01:51:33.777 --> 01:51:35.112
Down! We're getting down.

911
01:51:35.320 --> 01:51:37.739
Shut your eyes.
Shut your eyes. baby.

912
01:51:38.824 --> 01:51:40.492
Shut your eyes. Shut your eyes.

913
01:51:49.334 --> 01:51:51.503
Shut your eyes. Shut your eyes.

914
01:51:51.712 --> 01:51:55.215
It's just a bad dream.
It's just a bad dream.

915
01:52:43.889 --> 01:52:47.351
Why did she not take me
with the others?

916
01:52:49.228 --> 01:52:51.355
Because you're her mother.

917
01:52:56.276 --> 01:52:59.279
Mother is God in the eyes of a child.

918
01:53:27.391 --> 01:53:29.226
I love you.

919
01:54:38.337 --> 01:54:40.631
<i>- Hi. this is Chris.
- And this is Rose.</i>

920
01:54:40.839 --> 01:54:42.633
<i>And I'm Sharon Da Silva.</i>

921
01:54:42.841 --> 01:54:45.219
<i>Please leave a message!</i>

922
01:54:47.179 --> 01:54:49.765
Christopher. it's me.

923
01:54:50.349 --> 01:54:51.642
I'm with Sharon.

924
01:54:53.727 --> 01:54:57.105
Hello? Hello? Rose?

925
01:54:57.564 --> 01:54:59.024
Rose?

926
01:55:00.234 --> 01:55:02.820
Yeah. We're coming home.

927
01:55:03.305 --> 01:56:03.515
